Title: API: modification of password endpoints to return an object for create and update
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: core
Date: 1613120599
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

In the previous version, the create and update endpoints for passwords returned
a 204 status in case of a successful operation. This is changed to serve the password
with a 200 status code.
